'''強烈熱帶氣旋溫斯頓'''（英語：Severe Tropical Cyclone Winston）為[[2015－2016年南太平洋熱帶氣旋季|2015－2016年南太平洋熱帶氣旋季]]第4個被命名的風暴，是首個相當於[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风风力等级|薩菲爾-辛普森颶風等級]]之「五級颱風」強度[[登陸_(氣象學)|登陸]]斐濟的[[熱帶氣旋|熱帶氣旋]]。

溫斯頓是南半球有紀錄以來最強的熱帶氣旋，其10分鐘平均風速達150[[節_(單位)|節]]（每小時280公里），打破1979年[[台风泰培_(1979年)|颱風泰培]]之140節（每小時260公里）的紀錄；溫斯頓的中心最低[[氣壓|氣壓]]為884[[百帕斯卡|百帕斯卡]]，是南半球有紀錄以來氣壓最低的熱帶氣旋。

在暴風抵達斐濟之前，很多庇護所啟用，全國性的禁止外出命令於2月20日晚間發佈。2月20日以第五等級的強度侵襲斐濟，溫斯頓在許多島造成災害，以及44人死亡。至少6個島的通訊系統暫時失去作用。有些島甚至在暴風過境2天後仍然是通訊失聯的。總計有四萬個住所遭到損壞或毀壞，大約35萬人(約四成的斐濟人口)被該暴風衝擊。總共造成14億美金的損失。政府於2月20日發佈了60天的[[緊急狀態令|緊急狀態命令]]。在暴風之後，澳洲和紐西蘭政府提供後勤支援與救援物資。在接下來幾週，國際間與他國政府組織，帶來數千萬元的援助款與數百噸的物資給斐濟居民。

==背景==
斐濟雖然常受熱帶氣旋影響，但很少風暴能以薩菲爾-辛普森颶風等級之「五級颱風」強度吹襲斐濟。斐濟自1941年有紀錄以來，只有2012年強烈熱帶氣旋埃文曾以薩菲爾-辛普森颶風等級之「四級颱風」強度吹襲維提島的西岸，而斐濟有紀錄以來登陸時風速最高的熱帶氣旋為1985年熱帶氣旋奈傑。溫斯頓是自1979年熱帶氣旋Meli以來，令斐濟受災最嚴重的熱帶氣旋。

==氣象歷史==
{{storm path|Winston 2016 track.png}}
2016年2月7日，[[斐濟氣象局|斐濟氣象局]](FMS)開始監測熱帶擾動09F，生成於[[瓦努阿图|瓦努阿图]][[维拉港|维拉港]]西北方1000公里<ref name="TDS 7/2">{{cite web|title=Tropical Disturbance Summary for Area Equator to 25S, 160E to 120W Issued From RSMC Feb 072320 UTC|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6fBiTyQOw?url=http://gwydir.demon.co.uk/advisories/WWPS21-NFFN_201602072300.htm|publisher=Fiji Meteorological Service|accessdate=2016-02-19|url=http://www.met.gov.fj/aifs_prods/20036.txt|archivedate=2016-02-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，[[聯合颱風警報中心|聯合颱風警報中心]]於2月10日給予「低」之評級。

==影響==
氣旋溫斯頓於斐濟許多島嶼造成廣泛損害<ref name="RNZ1"/>，全國90萬人口中有80%面臨電力中斷<ref name="GuardianFeb21">{{cite news|author=Nadia Khomami|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2016-02-21|accessdate=2016-02-21|title=Cyclone Winston: Fiji counts deaths and damage from giant storm|url=http://www.theguardian.com/australia-news/2016/feb/20/cyclone-winston-virgin-australia-and-jetstar-cancel-services-to-and-from-fiji|archive-date=2016-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160221092903/http://www.theguardian.com/australia-news/2016/feb/20/cyclone-winston-virgin-australia-and-jetstar-cancel-services-to-and-from-fiji|dead-url=no}}</ref>，包括整個[[瓦努阿岛|瓦努阿岛]]<ref>{{cite web|author=Elenoa Turagaiviu|publisher=Fiji Broadcast Corporation|date=2016-02-21|accessdate=2016-02-21|title=Restoration of essential services is a priority url=http://www.fbc.com.fj/fiji/37744/restoration-of-essential-services-is-a-priority-}}</ref>，主要因颶風級強風吹倒樹木及輸電線<ref name="RNZ1">{{cite web|publisher=Radio New Zealand|date=2016-02-20|accessdate=2016-02-20|title=Winston leaves trail of destruction|url=http://www.radionz.co.nz/news/world/297041/winston-leaves-trail-of-destruction|archive-date=2020-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200727015549/https://www.rnz.co.nz/news/world/297041/let-us-pray-for-our-nation-bainimarama|dead-url=no}}</ref>，斐濟全國共計43人死亡，其中21人於西部大區，14人位於東部大區，6人於中部大區及2人位於北部大區<ref>{{cite report|work=United Nations Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs|publisher=ReliefWeb|date=2016-02-27|accessdate=2016-02-27|title=Fiji: Severe Tropical Cyclone Winston Situation Report No. 7 (as of 27 February 2016)|url=http://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/OCHA%20TC%20Winston%20Situation%20Report%207.pdf|format=PDF|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304101406/http://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/OCHA%20TC%20Winston%20Situation%20Report%207.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=Losalini Bolatagici|newspaper=Fiji Times|date=2016-02-25|accessdate=2016-02-25|title=44 now confirmed dead|url=http://fijitimes.com/story.aspx?id=343159|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305131301/http://fijitimes.com/story.aspx?id=343159|archive-date=2016-03-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=Losalini Bolatagici|newspaper=Fiji Times|date=2016-02-29|accessdate=2016-02-29|title=TC Winston death toll rises to 43|url=http://fijitimes.com/story.aspx?id=343731|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307031908/http://fijitimes.com/story.aspx?id=343731|archive-date=2016-03-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。[[馬圖庫島|馬圖庫島]]固網電話中斷<ref>{{cite web|author=Tokasa Rainima|publisher=Fiji Broadcasting Corporation|date=2016-02-20|accessdate=2016-02-20|title=Matuku prepares for bad weather|url=http://www.fbc.com.fj/fiji/37691/matuku-prepares-for-bad-weather|archive-date=2016-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160221094945/http://www.fbc.com.fj/fiji/37691/matuku-prepares-for-bad-weather|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

斐濟[[东部大区|东部大区]]約有150棟房屋毀損，另有60棟遭不同程度破壞<ref name="sitrep1">{{cite report|author1=UN Office for the Coordination of Human Affairs|title=Fiji: Severe Tropical Cyclone Winston Situation Report No. 1 (as of 21 February 2016)|url=https://www.humanitarianresponse.info/en/node/120198|publisher=ReliefWeb|accessdate=2016-02-21|format=PDF|date=2016-02-21|type=Situation report|archive-date=2016-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160302143016/https://www.humanitarianresponse.info/en/node/120198|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[西部大区|西部大区]]校園所受損失為220萬[[斐濟元|斐濟元]]（103萬美元）<ref>{{cite web|author=Farzana Nisha|publisher=Fiji Broadcast Corporation|date=2016-02-23|accessdate=2016-02-23|title=$2.2m in damages estimated for western schools|url=http://www.fbc.com.fj/fiji/37799/2-2m-in-damages-estimated-for-western-schools|archive-date=2016-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160302141904/http://www.fbc.com.fj/fiji/37799/2-2m-in-damages-estimated-for-western-schools|dead-url=no}}</ref>，製糖工業則損失8300萬斐濟元（3890萬美元）<ref>{{cite news|author=Felix Chaudhary|newspaper=Fiji Times|date=2016-02-23|accessdate=2016-02-23|title=$83m initial damage to sugar industry|url=http://fijitimes.com/story.aspx?id=342856|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304200340/http://fijitimes.com/story.aspx?id=342856|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

斐濟所有學校因设施損壞嚴重，而停課一至二週<ref>{{cite web|author=Ritika Pratap|publisher=Fiji Broadcast Corporation|date=2016-02-21|accessdate=2016-02-21|title=Schools to go on one week break|url=http://www.fbc.com.fj/fiji/37742/schools-to-go-on-one-week-break-|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160221090431/http://www.fbc.com.fj/fiji/37742/schools-to-go-on-one-week-break-|archive-date=2016-02-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Aliki Bia|publisher=Fiji Broadcast Corporation|date=2016-02-22|accessdate=2016-02-22|title=PM gives rural schools two weeks break|url=http://www.fbc.com.fj/fiji/37790/pm-gives-rural-schools-two-weeks-break|archive-date=2016-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160223104907/http://www.fbc.com.fj/fiji/37790/pm-gives-rural-schools-two-weeks-break|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。該國主要機場[[楠迪國際機場|楠迪國際機場]]因氣旋關閉2日<ref>{{Cite web|title = Cyclone Winston: Clean-up begins as death toll jumps to 20|url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-35628181|website = BBC News|access-date = 2016-02-22|archive-date = 2016-02-22|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160222133229/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-35628181|dead-url = no}}</ref>。至2月23日上午，全國約22,000人暫居於50個避難所，其中僅西部大區即達19,294人<ref>{{cite news|author=Losalini Roasoqosoqo|newspaper=Fiji Times|date=2016-02-22|accessdate=2016-02-22|title=8438 people in evacuation centres|url=http://fijitimes.com/story.aspx?id=342700|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160223104630/http://www.fijitimes.com/story.aspx?id=342700|archive-date=2016-02-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=Felix Chaudhary|newspaper=Fiji Times|date=2016-02-23|accessdate=2016-02-23|title=13,000 people in evacuation centres in West|url=http://fijitimes.com/story.aspx?id=342857|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304194517/http://fijitimes.com/story.aspx?id=342857|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

